Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術是將物質理解分解並且再構築的科學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不是萬能的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不能從無中誕生物質
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須付出相應的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是鍊金術的基本 等價交換
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術師有一個禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是人體鍊成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是任何人都不能侵犯的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯·休斯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被身上紋了咬尾蛇刺青的神秘人物殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯坦古對這一血案懷有疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了這件事和軍隊上層部有關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次決意進入中央
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不知道的愛德和阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與溫莉一起向著師傅所在的城市達普利斯前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著南部開始了旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}拉修巴雷的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉修巴雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛斯的11年式造型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到有一天能親眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是機械鎧的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒理由非得在這大熱天裡觀賞機械鎧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔下溫莉早點去達普利斯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟 打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個機械鎧的形狀很稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦 大家也都來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下 住手 住…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 那裡 那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都熱心於研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 所以才說機械鎧技師這些人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家鍊金術師的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是帕妮孃幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮孃？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專找觀光客下手的小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那傢伙現在在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 相對地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我們看一下小哥的機械鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在一個叫多明尼克的機械鎧技師那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說為了能採掘優質的礦石而住在深山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條路真的是對的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會被騙了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追根究底 還不是因為妳想去那個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀懷錶被偷是因為你自己不注意吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 你們倆看下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會到處躲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 呼吸變急促了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妳很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西在這裡並不稀奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左腳是1.5英寸加爾巴林炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來抓我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會讓妳逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別放她走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 絕對不放開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,750)}（捏緊）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那機械鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在讓我仔細看清楚之前是絕對不放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮孃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種機械鎧 第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說懸掛裝置也很高級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼看 這個全體的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒有多餘的設計
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我的銀懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做出這種機械鎧 我真的很佩服你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個不是我製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得有點重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給裝備者加上負擔可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這小子才那麼矮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說我矮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 弄得再輕一點的話 我的身高也會長高？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真矮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多明尼克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收我為弟子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微想一想也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 我不收弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就教她如何做出能讓我長高的機械鎧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 爸爸很頑固
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水蚤 水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 是小寶寶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能摸摸妳的肚子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前也像這樣呆在媽媽的肚子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣不好 關節就痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼裝上了機械鎧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被捲進列車事故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙親都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有可以依靠的人 再加上不能走路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就像是世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個時候 遇到了多明尼克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副自己是這個世上最不幸的人似的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種人最讓人生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開 放開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我的表情一定很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 莫名其妙地就被裝上了機械鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術痛死了 恢復訓練辛苦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用雙腳站在大地上的時候 我非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很感謝多明尼克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算花費一生來報答他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還一次都沒有收過我錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才 偷竊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要感謝他的話 就不要再偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個雙腳是多明尼克先生的誠意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 妳也必須用誠意來報答他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說要用一生來報答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要偷竊 實實在在地站起來工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用妳那雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣 多明尼克先生也一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏踏實實地工作來還這個情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 要去還了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 難道弄壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋子打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是用鍊金術把蓋子蓋上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是顯然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為裡面有被看到了就會很害臊的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來看看愛德的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「別忘了 11年10月3日」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個還給愛德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求多明尼克先生收我為弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬 馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要生了 莎特拉太太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的雨 沒法帶去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跑一趟把醫生叫過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸馬上就會把醫生帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一下 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說忍… 但是要生的時候還是會生出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼 聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 沒有醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們自己來做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有接生的經驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也沒有猶豫的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家協力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德和阿爾去燒熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮孃把所有的毛巾找來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 理多爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有消毒用的酒精
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉庫裡應該有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 把飲用水放在莎特拉太太的枕邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她來做不會有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是在醫生之家出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小就把家裡的醫學書當畫冊一樣看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說 沒有真正學過？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計只是記得一個大概的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在只有依靠她的知識和膽量了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒開水 消毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來 快想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮孃 妳進來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵的時候 我是多麼地無力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 痛 痛 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（怕 怕 怕）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說不存在神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有現在 拜託他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血 血…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出 出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真的出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 厲害 厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 厲害地叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只有那種小孩子一樣的感想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這可是生命的誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術師研究了幾百年還沒有成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類製造人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把生命的神秘和鍊金術做比較
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 是我的職業病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 孩子平安地出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後還有要我做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我拉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（腰軟了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓比自己矮的男孩子背 真是恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說就把妳扔地上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷看了銀懷錶裡的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行打開的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒讓阿爾看過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對自己的警告和覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真是沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天的事情 必須要用這種形式帶在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是妳在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是妳在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們兄弟倆都不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我代替你們哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是回鄉下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆一個人會寂寞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看到了愛德的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能只抱著半吊子的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不需要連妳也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要進一步加強自己的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你用上更好的機械鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了愛德能安心地繼續旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我再次去求多明尼克先生收我為弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理多爾先生想讓妳過去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕妮孃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 快點把懷錶還給我 妳這小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不需要用右手打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用左手再打一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爺爺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色完全變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（嬌寵 嬌寵）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母子的健康狀況良好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產後的處理也很適當
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接生這種事 連大人也會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我已經拚命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是受大伙照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼鄭重的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒招了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（靈機一動）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 現在就收個弟子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個和那個是兩碼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不收弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳無論如何都想做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以給妳介紹一個住在山腳下的好技師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾來參觀你的工作 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾來看看我的孫子 那倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的野丫頭也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯過這班的話 下趟去達普利斯的就是三天後了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬事小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給婆婆打電話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被你說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要好好偷學那個老頭子的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面的時候給我裝個更好的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在師傅居住的城市 達普利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年們回想起修行的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是走向真理的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.19,0:24:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12話 一即是全 全即是一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.13,0:24:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶豫的言語
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為想保護自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}不必消去這份記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:35.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}人生不是還很漫長？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}那些沒有做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:42.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}只是想重新做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:58.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}明明一直在追趕著夢的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:05.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}跌跌撞撞地走在彎曲的小道上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:08.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}不奢望回到那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:11.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}只是在苦尋那片丟失的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:13.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就像你明白一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:18.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}除去那像犧牲之後的悲傷表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:20.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}罪孽之後並不是淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}而是一直以來背負的苦難
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}迷失在沒有出口的情感迷宮中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在等待著誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:27.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}就像在白色筆記本上刻畫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}很想誠實地說出心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}在逃避什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:32.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}…原來是叫做現實的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}為了實現願望而活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}不禁想要大喊  你能聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:43.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}平安無事卻讓人沒法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:45.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}…無家可歸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:49.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}感謝同伴們帶來的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:51.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以要更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}讓人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.47,0:01:57.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur6}這種痛苦也不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:32.97,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur6}那天看到的緋紅天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:38.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.18,0:22:44.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}約定和契約  被初夏的微風所懷抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:48.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}兩個人互相依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:57.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在強顏歡笑的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:02.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}隱藏著逐漸擴大的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:12.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以  只裝做沒有發現  選擇了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:21.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}在桌邊繼續等待那沒有震撼的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:29.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在空白的夜裡  無法迎接的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:34.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}其實我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.69,0:23:40.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}那天看到的緋紅天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.32,0:23:45.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}總有一天會想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:51.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6}抱著沒有實現的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:55.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}兩個人一起出發
